  "text": "Excuse me guys question for you sir. Who's the richest person here? Have you heard of Pepsi Pepsi the soda company? Yes, we just sold our company to them for almost two billion dollars to Billy with a V Yes with the V so you guys work together you guys are business partners. You could say that she's also my wife You guys are you guys are married? Yeah still married after the business actually Yeah, I go all over the world and you've been billionaires to help the younger generation I can admit it with you for the channel real quick. Do you guys have any kids? We do kids Yeah, so your balance in multi-billion dollar company a marriage and also having children Go in the world. Did you balance all of that? There's no such thing as balance. There's spreadsheets in the bedsheets We maxed out our credit cards. We did everything we could to survive Did you guys scale super quickly or was it a long day? No, so poppies the fastest growing beverage in the history of beverage from zero to 500 million only took us five years Are you serious? Yes. What's the five years? We launched during COVID. We were one of the first brands to get on tiktok I have over three billion views on my face on tiktok. Brands were getting killed during COVID Yeah, but you know what you can have a fantastic product, but if your brand is shit, you're not gonna be successful Do you guys think people should do business with their significant other or is it not for the week? It's definitely not for the week I wouldn't advise against it because I mean look at us We built and sold the business for near the two billion dollars and built a family and the biggest thing is marriage is not 50 50 A business partnership is not 50 50 each person has to be committed a hundred percent because at any given time Someone's gonna be falling short of a hundred percent trust and commitment are absolutely critical. How do you all today? I'm 38 Older a little bit older a little bit older a little bit wiser So let me ask y'all this if the three of us died tomorrow and you could be one more message with the younger generation leave one more message With your children right here. What would that be? I think it was Steve Jobs that said this this world was created by people no smarter than you and I and so if you Have a dream just put in the work and go get it I think embarrassment is the most under explored emotion when it comes to success a lot of people ask Why are you so confident Allison? I embarrassed myself repeatedly until I gained confidence. So go make a fool of yourself. You guys have amazing advice Thank you. I connect with all the billionaires that I interviewed I get you guys's contact",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.1,
      "text": "Excuse me guys question for you sir. Who's the richest person here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 4.2,
      "end": 6.6,
      "text": "Have you heard of Pepsi Pepsi the soda company?"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.8,
      "end": 11.0,
      "text": "Yes, we just sold our company to them for almost two billion dollars to Billy with a V"
    },
    {
      "start": 11.0,
      "end": 15.3,
      "text": "Yes with the V so you guys work together you guys are business partners. You could say that she's also my wife"
    },
    {
      "start": 15.3,
      "end": 18.3,
      "text": "You guys are you guys are married? Yeah still married after the business actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 18.3,
      "end": 21.1,
      "text": "Yeah, I go all over the world and you've been billionaires to help the younger generation"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.1,
      "end": 24.7,
      "text": "I can admit it with you for the channel real quick. Do you guys have any kids? We do kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.7,
      "end": 29.6,
      "text": "Yeah, so your balance in multi-billion dollar company a marriage and also having children"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.6,
      "end": 34.9,
      "text": "Go in the world. Did you balance all of that? There's no such thing as balance. There's spreadsheets in the bedsheets"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.9,
      "end": 38.6,
      "text": "We maxed out our credit cards. We did everything we could to survive"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.6,
      "end": 41.1,
      "text": "Did you guys scale super quickly or was it a long day?"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.2,
      "end": 47.4,
      "text": "No, so poppies the fastest growing beverage in the history of beverage from zero to 500 million only took us five years"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.4,
      "end": 49.6,
      "text": "Are you serious? Yes. What's the five years?"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.7,
      "end": 53.3,
      "text": "We launched during COVID. We were one of the first brands to get on tiktok"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.3,
      "end": 57.1,
      "text": "I have over three billion views on my face on tiktok. Brands were getting killed during COVID"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.1,
      "end": 62.8,
      "text": "Yeah, but you know what you can have a fantastic product, but if your brand is shit, you're not gonna be successful"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.8,
      "end": 66.3,
      "text": "Do you guys think people should do business with their significant other or is it not for the week?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.4,
      "end": 67.5,
      "text": "It's definitely not for the week"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.5,
      "end": 69.6,
      "text": "I wouldn't advise against it because I mean look at us"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.6,
      "end": 75.1,
      "text": "We built and sold the business for near the two billion dollars and built a family and the biggest thing is marriage is not 50 50"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.1,
      "end": 80.2,
      "text": "A business partnership is not 50 50 each person has to be committed a hundred percent because at any given time"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.2,
      "end": 85.8,
      "text": "Someone's gonna be falling short of a hundred percent trust and commitment are absolutely critical. How do you all today? I'm 38"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.2,
      "end": 89.7,
      "text": "Older a little bit older a little bit older a little bit wiser"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.2,
      "end": 97.6,
      "text": "So let me ask y'all this if the three of us died tomorrow and you could be one more message with the younger generation leave one more message"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.6,
      "end": 99.2,
      "text": "With your children right here. What would that be?"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.3,
      "end": 103.5,
      "text": "I think it was Steve Jobs that said this this world was created by people no smarter than you and I and so if you"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.5,
      "end": 105.3,
      "text": "Have a dream just put in the work and go get it"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.3,
      "end": 111.3,
      "text": "I think embarrassment is the most under explored emotion when it comes to success a lot of people ask"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.3,
      "end": 112.6,
      "text": "Why are you so confident Allison?"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.6,
      "end": 118.7,
      "text": "I embarrassed myself repeatedly until I gained confidence. So go make a fool of yourself. You guys have amazing advice"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.7,
      "end": 122.5,
      "text": "Thank you. I connect with all the billionaires that I interviewed I get you guys's contact"
    }
